@node Future "Things for future releases"

Future
------

Lots can be added. This is just an initial version. Further developement
will depend on the sort of response I receive. Here are a few ideas
for the future.


- Better updating of the list

- Quit/Hide choice, allowing Task Control to be in memory at all times.

- Show all Tasks button

- Configurable hide list

- Configurable alias list. A couple are already pre-defined. dopus_task
  will appear as Directory Opus.



@endnode

